column2: SELECT    s.specObjID, s.ra, s.dec, s.z as redshift, s.zErr, s.class, s.zWarning, s.snMedian, g.ra, g.dec, p.modelMag_u, p.modelMag_g, p.modelMag_r, p.modelMag_i, p.modelMag_z,   p.err_u, p.err_g, p.err_r, p.err_i, p.err_z, p.petroR5#_g, p.petroR5#_r, p.petroR5#_i, p.petroR5#Err_g, p.petroR5#Err_r, p.petroR5#Err_i, p.petroR9#_g, p.petroR9#_r,   p.petroR9#_i, p.petroR9#Err_g, p.petroR9#Err_r, p.petroR9#Err_i into mydb.result_zoo3 from mydb.zoo2Main as g        CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestSpecObjEq( g.ra, g.dec, #) AS near    JOIN SpecObjAll as s ON near.specObjID=s.specObjID   JOIN PhotoObjAll as p ON p.objID = s.bestObjID
